 Nov. 17 through Dec. 30. \u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eLocated at 150 Bay Parkway in Wantagh, the all-ages event will take guests on a journey through more than 2 million lights with various scenes including Mattel’s 32-foot tall Barbie, Prehistoric Christmas, Big Foot Monster Trucks and the Snow Flurry Tunnel.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eReturning favorites include the 12 Days of Christmas, Toyland and the Enchanting Tunnel of Lights.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eStop in the Jolly Holiday Village to see illuminated trees, take pictures with Santa, visit concessions and more.\u0026nbsp;Kids can print out a letter to Santa and drop it off at the mailbox.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eTickets are currently $30 per vehicle and can be purchased in advance at \u003ca href=\"https://concerts.livenation.com/magic-of-lights-drivethrough-holiday-lights-wantagh-new-york-12-30-2023/event/1D005F47D61F1DDB?_gl=1*1yx8hoa*_gcl_au*MTI2MDU3NTczLjE2OTk2MzQ1Mjc.*_ga*NDE2MDY0ODQ4LjE2OTk2MzQ1Mjk.*_ga_H1KKSGW33X*MTY5OTY1NDQyMy4yLjEuMTY5OTY1NDQyNy4wLjAuMA..*_ga_72VVKN21YG*MTY5OTY1NDQyMy4yLjEuMTY5OTY1NDQyNy4wLjAuMA..\u0026amp;_ga=2.26824510.2081419304.1699634529-416064848.1699634529\"\u003elivenation.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003e\u0026quot;Magic of Lights\u0026quot; will be open Sundays through Thursdays from 5 to 10 p.m., and Fridays and Saturdays from 5 to 11 p.m.\u003c/p\u003e","publishedDate":"2023-11-16T10:00:00Z","updatedDate":"2023-11-17T19:51:40.810Z","url":"https://www.newsday.com/lifestyle/holidays/winter-holidays/jones-beach-magic-lights-2023-iu8g9a7x","headline":"Jones Beach 'Magic of Lights' returns for the 2023 holiday season ","teaserTitle":"The Jones Beach holiday lights show returns this weekend","newsLabel":"none","newsLabel2":"none","subType":"article","gridFilter":[],"contentPath":[{"id":"contentid/Newsday.Lifestyle.d","title":"Things to Do","path":"/lifestyle","__typename":"Section"},{"id":"contentid/Newsday.Lifestyle.Holidays.d","title":