8r","newsLabel":"none","newsLabel2":"none","svgLogo":"","timeToRead":"","topElement":{"__typename":"Image","id":"contentid/NDYyODg2MzEtNGZlMi00","width":1601,"height":2400,"title":"FAPHOTOS231113_photos","headline":"","baseUrl":"https://cdn.newsday.com/image-service/version/c:MGZlNmU3ZWMtNzIyZi00:YzI4OGJj/faphotos231113_photos.jpg","caption":"\u003cp\u003e\n\tYaquelin Jerez, Eddy Jerez, Jeisly Jerez, 14, and Eddilyn Jerez, 19, of Riverhead take Christmas photos at Long Island Selfie Studio in Riverhead\u0026nbsp;Nov. 5.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n","altTag":"","byline":"Morgan Campbell","organization":"","floatLeft":false,"floatRight":false,"imageSize":"","useFreeform":false},"topMediaItem":null,"relatedLinks":[]}},{"id":"contentid/ZjI1ZTZiMTUtNjVhYi00","__typename":"Teaser","title":"10 events, things to do this weekend on LI","teaserOvertitle":null,"text":"Options include festivals, family-friendly fun, concerts and more.","longText":"","customLogo":null,"media":{"__typename":"Image","id":"contentid/YWY0ZmQ0NGYtODYzMy00","width":1494,"height":1845,"title":"events2022  delguidice","headline":"","baseUrl":"https://cdn.newsday.com/image-service/version/c:OThmMWViNzUtZGMwZS00:MWZiZDA3/events2022-delguidice.jpg","caption":"\u003cp\u003e\n\tMichael DelGuidice channels Billy Joel when he plays with his popular tribute band, Big Shot.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n","altTag":"","byline":"Bruce Gilbert","organization":"","floatLeft":false,"floatRight":false,"imageSize":"","useFreeform":false},"content":{"__typename":"Article","id":"contentid/OGU5MGVhZWEtZTNhNS00","lead":"Options include festivals, family-friendly fun, concerts and more.","body":"\u003cp\u003eIf you're looking for things to do on Long Island, here are spots to explore and events to attend this weekend.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eDISNEY ON ICE\u0026nbsp;AT UBS ARENA\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eSee all of your favorite Disney stars on ice with the debut of Raya from “Raya and the Last Dragon” and Elsa and Anna from “Frozen 2” along with\u0026nbsp;Woody and Buzz, Moana, Mirabel and other favorites, 7 p.m. Nov. 15-16;\u0026nbsp;11 a.m. and 7 p.m. Nov. 17; 11 a.m., 3 and 7 p.m. Nov. 18-19. Tickets start at $33.45, parking starts at $20;\u0026nbsp;2400 Hempstead Tpke., Elmont,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"http://ubsarena.com\"\u003eubsarena.com\u003c/a\u003e, 516-460-8950.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eMIKE DELGUIDICE AT THE PARAMOUNT\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eThe singer/songwriter who tours with Billy Joel performs with his band, 8 p.m. Nov. 17. Tickets start at $32.75; 370 New York Ave., Huntington,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"http://paramountny.com\"\u003eparamountny.com\u003c/a\u003e, 631-673-7300.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eNORTH FORK TV FESTIVAL\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eSee screenings of award winning pilots from the 2023 Independent TV and Pilot Competition, Q\u0026amp;A panel with the creators and writers and more, two sessions: 3:30 to 5 p.m. and 7 to 8:30 p.m. Nov. 18 at Borghese Vineyard. Tickets start at $50; 17150 Country Road 48, Cutchogue,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"http://northfork.tv\"\u003enorthfork.tv\u003c/a\u003e, 631-213-1316.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eMAGIC OF LIGHTS AT JONES BEACH\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eDrive-thru takes you around paths with sparkling lights, holiday-themed displays along with the Big Foot Monster Truck display and Barbie display, you can visit a concession stand and stop by the Jolly Holiday Village and see an array of trees, 5 to 10 p.m. Sunday through Thursday and 5 to 11 p.m. Friday through Saturday from Nov. 17 through Dec. 30. Tickets range $25-$40; Ocean Parkway, Wantagh, advanced tickets available online at \u003ca href=\"http://magicoflights.com\"\u003emagicoflights.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eBETHPAGE TURKEY DRIVE\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eDonate frozen turkeys, non-perishable food items or cash donations, benefits the Island Harvest Food Bank, 7:30 a.m. to 6 p.m. Nov. 17 at Bethpage Federal Credit Union;\u0026nbsp;899 South Oyster Bay Rd., Bethpage, \u003ca href=\"https://bethpagefcu.com/community/turkey-drive/\"\u003ebethpagefcu.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eBROOKHAVEN POLAR PLUNGE\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eTake the\u0026nbsp;plunge, registration at 9:30 a.m. Nov. 18, plunge at 11:30 a.m. at Cedar Beach. Donations accepted and benefits Special Olympics New York;\u0026nbsp;244 Harbor Beach Rd., Mt. Sinai,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"http://events.nyso.org\"\u003eevents.nyso.org\u003c/a\u003e.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eTURKEY TRAIL TROT\u0026nbsp;AT BETHPAGE STATE PARK\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eGet ready for the annual trot that welcomes runners and walkers for a 5k run/walk through the trails followed by post-race treats, race begins at 9:30 a.m. Nov. 18; a free Kiddie Dash precedes at 9 a.m. Registration is $35, enter at Plainview and Manchester, drive pass the toll both, parking lot is on the left and then walk up to the polo field,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://events.elitefeats.com/23trailtrot\"\u003eevents.elitefeats.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eLEANN RIMES\u0026nbsp;AT THE STALLER CENTER\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eThe country singer performs, 8 p.m. Nov. 18 at Stony Brook University. Tickets start at $62; 100 Nicolls Rd., Stony Brook,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://stallercenter.showare.com/eventperformances.asp?evt=346\"\u003estallercenter.showare.com\u003c/a\u003e, 631-632-2787.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eHOWIE MANDEL AT NYCB THEATRE\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eCatch the comedian when he brings his talents to the stage, 8 p.m. Nov. 19. Tickets start at $28;\u0026nbsp;960 Brush Hollow Rd., Westbury, \u003ca href=\"https://www.livenation.com/event/k7vGF9NL_F4XH/howie-mandel\"\u003econcerts.livenation.com\u003c/a\u003e, 516-247-5200.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003ch2\u003eMUSIC LOVERS FAIR\u0026nbsp;IN MASSAPEQUA\u003c/h2\u003e \n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll find vinyl records, compact discs, DVDs and music memorabilia on display and for sale, 10 a.m. to 3 p.m. Nov. 19 at the American Legion Post 1066. $5; 66 Veterans Blvd., Massapequa,\u0026nbsp;\u003ca href=\"http://showsandexpos.com\"\u003eshowsandexpos.com\u003c/a\u003e, 973-209-6067.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_1945E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_1943S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_1945S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2331S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2334S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2334E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2260E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2256E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_2253E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_927S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_930S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_932S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_936S\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_936E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_932E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_930E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"cke_bm_927E\" style=\"display: none;\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","publishedDate":"2020-04-23T09:00: